headline: Garmin named Supplier of the Year by Cirrus Aircraft at PX25
summary: Garmin (NYSE: GRMN) is proud to announce it received the prestigious Supplier of the Year honor from Cirrus Aircraft at PX25, their Supplier Conference held February 26 in Knoxville, Tennessee. Cirrus Aircraft, an aerospace leader in personal aviation, recognizes one strategic supplier that has exemplified outstanding performance, innovation and collaboration, playing a crucial role in advancing Cirrus's mission and vision.
